text: Taxi to Heaven () is a 1943 Soviet comedy movie directed by Gerbert Rappaport.Кинематограф Великой Отечественной войны: время героев и гениевВоздушный извозчик (1943) It stars Mikhail Zharov, Lyudmila Tselikovskaya, and Boris Blinov. == Actors == * Mikhail Zharov as Baranov * Lyudmila Tselikovskaya as Natasha * Boris Blinov as The Colonel * Grigoriy Shpigel as Svellovidov * Vladimir Gribkov as Kulikov (as V.
